-- 2012-06-28T23:53:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/fed-s-fisher-says-health-care-ruling-increases-clarity.html
Federal  Reserve Bank  of Dallas
President Richard Fisher said he isn’t worried that China will
use the threat of selling Treasuries to gain an advantage in its
relations with the U.S.  “They’ll invest according to prudent investment
measures,” Fisher said today in Aspen, Colorado. “We’re the
most attractive place for sovereign credit risk.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
